org.perfidix.result

Class BenchmarkResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfidix.result.AbstractResult
      • org.perfidix.result.AbstractResultContainer<ClassResult>
        • org.perfidix.result.BenchmarkResult

  • public final class BenchmarkResult
extends AbstractResultContainer<ClassResult>
    This class holds the data of a complete Benchmark. Only one BenchmarkResult is generated per Benchmark-Run. The different components are ClassResult objects. This class is the container for the results of a Benchmark and therefore the input for different Outputs.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz, Alexander Onea, neue Couch
    See Also:
    Benchmark, AbstractOutput
